Rochester.Rochester Township, Olmsted County, Minn:
Rochester Township is a township in Olmsted County, Minnesota, United States. The population was 2,916 at the 2000 census.


== Geography ==
According to the United States Census Bureau, the township has a total area of 22.3 square miles (57.9 km²), of which 22.3 square miles (57.8 km²) of it is land and 0.04 square miles (0.1 km²) of it (0.09%) is water.
